## User Story

As a **user**, I want to **search for items based on keywords**, so that I can quickly find the items I need.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: The search bar should accept keywords and return relevant items.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: The results should be sorted by relevance.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Add search functionality to the back-end.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Implement search UI in the front-end.
- [ ] **Task 3**: Implement sorting by relevance.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: Medium
- **Related Issues**: #102
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Consider adding auto-suggestions to improve user experience.
